<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>My suggested spell lineup:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1815&amp;source=Live">Flames of Ro</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (400dd fire LURE)<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2672&amp;source=Live">Fiery Curse</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (-38 fire resist on target)<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1198&amp;source=Live">Ro's Shadowed Flame</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (Decrease AC 27, Fire Resist 68, and ATK 62)<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=1367&amp;source=Live">Fiery Might</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (Self-only hp regen + damage shield)<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=2202&amp;source=Live">Mana Shield</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (Self rune)<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://lucy.fnord.net/spell.html?id=659&amp;source=Live">Conflagration</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (625dd fire)<br>
<br>
Now, with the exception of Conflagration, those are all NPC-only spells (or weapon procs), so no classes should complain.  Also, that spell lineup gives them quite a bit of destructive/utility power without making them unbalanced. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=59003"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.nc.rr.com/jelong/users/web/Cedrich/rofl.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
